Mandatory questions  
You probably don't get these questions every day.Yet as a bank we have to impose them

Income

Next one  
 
Deposit or withdraw cash  
 
How much cash do you expect to deposit per year?  
Choose an option:  
 Less than €10,000  
 Between €10,000 and €20,000

How much cash do you expect to withdraw per year?

Finally

 Yes

Place the phone on the top of the document. Do not move the document and the

This allows us to see whether you are the person on the ID. We keep a short 
recording of the scan. We do this so that we ca n demonstrate that you have been  
correctly identified.   
I agree to take and save this facial scan.
